headline.print_headline: Australian 'Counter-Terrorism' Raids Foil Beheading Plot: Media
headline.main: Australian 'Counter-Terrorism' Raids Foil Beheading Plot: Media

lead_paragraph: Australian police will allege that members of a group targeted in a sweeping counter-terrorism operation on Thursday planned to behead a random member of the public after draping the victim in the flag of Islamic State militants, Australia media reported.
